<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NS Tools Repository</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        h1 { color: #333; }
        h2 { color: #666; margin-top: 30px; }
        code {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        pre {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .package-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .package-list li {
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 3px solid #007bff;
        }
        .package-list a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .package-list a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>NS Tools APT Repository</h1>
    <p>Debian packages for NS Serial Tools suite</p>

    <h2>Quick Setup</h2>
    <pre><code># Add the repository
echo "deb [trusted=yes] https://yourcompany.github.io/ns-tools stable main" | \
    sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ns-tools.list

# Update and install
sudo apt update
sudo apt install ns-serial-mux ns-agent ns-ui</code></pre>

    <h2>Available Packages</h2>
    <ul class="package-list">
        <li>
            <strong>ns-serial-mux</strong> - Serial port multiplexer
            <br><a href="pool/main/ns-serial-mux_1.0.0_amd64.deb">Download v1.0.0</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>ns-agent</strong> - SNMP agent for NS tools
            <br><a href="pool/main/ns-agent_1.0.0_amd64.deb">Download v1.0.0</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>ns-ui</strong> - Web UI for NS tools
            <br><a href="pool/main/ns-ui_1.0.0_all.deb">Download v1.0.0</a>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Manual Installation</h2>
    <p>Download individual .deb files and install with:</p>
    <pre><code>sudo apt install ./package-name.deb</code></pre>

    <h2>Repository Structure</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="pool/main/">pool/main/</a> - Package files</li>
        <li><a href="dists/stable/">dists/stable/</a> - Repository metadata</li>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>